title: Comic Con-The Howard Stern Stories
description:
Comic Con-The Howard Stern Stories JUL 31 2015 Fri  (01:30:18)

Jon Hein talks to some of the stars, directors and creators of Howard's favorite movies, television shows and comic books! And you'll hear in their own words the impact the King of All Media has on the featured players shaping American culture today.

* Director Quentin Tarantino.
* Actor Rob Corddry (CHILDREN'S HOSPITAL) & SNL's Bobby Moynihan.
* Screenwriter Carlton Cuse. (LOST, THE STRAIN)
* Director Guillermo del Toro.
* Actor Bryan Cranston & Comic Book Writer Zeb Wells.
* Actor, Comedian, & Writer Derek Waters.(DRUNK HISTORY)
* Actor Jay Ferguson (Stan from MAD MEN).
* Dan Harmon, Ryan Ridley & Justin Roiland (Adult Swim's RICK & MORTY).
* The Cast Of TV Show GOTHAM.
* The IMPRACTICAL JOKERS cast.
* Actors Lucy Lawless (XENA) & Bruce Campbell (EVIL DEAD).
* Comic Book Artist, Writer, Editor & Publisher Jim Lee.
* Actor Michael Rosenbaum (IMPASTOR,SMALLVILLE)
* Director M.Night Shyamalan & Producer Jason Blum.
* The WORKAHOLICS guys.
* Director Eli Roth & His Actress Wife Lorenza Izzo.
* Actor, Comedian, Writer, Director & producer Paul Scheer.
* Actors Rami Malek & Christian Slater (Mr. ROBOT).
* Actor Zachary Levi & David Coleman (The Nerd Machine).
* Mike Tyson & Producer Hugh Davidson
